{"tid":1307822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家唔好講風涼說話，呢一刻更加要齊上齊落！","createTime":"2019-07-11T17:13:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T23:51:58.000Z","uid":2617,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"18e2f335fe6d23cfda84b5d21404e8e4f8333f18","tid":1307822,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:13:07.000Z","msg":"首先我見到手足比人打好心痛<br />\n大家唔好咁傻仔企定定比人打<br />\n一個已經嫌多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記住<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一係就避免群眾鬥群眾閃左去<br />\n一係就齊齊自衛 救到人就走</span></span><br />\n唔好眷戀個牆<br />\n牆係死 人係生<br />\n<br />\n但係我唔明點解有師兄可以幸災樂禍<br />\n你覺得佢企定定係on9<br />\n你咪屌佢 鬧醒佢<br />\n做咩要講風涼說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又話咩抵死 又話由佢地死<br />\n<br />\n希望大家明白<br />\n講呢D野對士氣對抗爭冇幫助的<br />\n我地可以走到呢一刻<br />\n全靠大家一齊努力<br />\n唔好因為呢D因群眾鬥群眾（呢D又唔係主線）<br />\n引發出既討論<br />\n搞到大家士氣下降<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家繼續努力<br />\n接下來仲有好漫長既抗爭活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n需要各位勇武同和理非巴絲努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求+雙普選 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n謝謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8106ccc91a82ce9332074841d01fc1f883883349","tid":1307822,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597c5d7e63985c49ace327b97400f25ca915a1c3","tid":1307822,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8106ccc91a82ce9332074841d01fc1f883883349","tid":1307822,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:14:11.000Z","msg":"仲唔訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3b6711ae6146b9f62f909a1ff660f03ef2ecf0f","tid":1307822,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:14:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">立即停手，我而家嚴重警告你，唔好再襲擊<br />\n<br />\n我而家係制止你再打人，請立即停手<br />\n<br />\n我而家係公民拘捕你，因為你對我朋友施以實質傷害的襲擊</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"7bc5fa7a131b0a62e599ef7663ee81492534d121","tid":1307822,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:15:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無論你選擇還手定係走佬<br />\n我地都會幫你說項 幫你spin<br />\n因為我地係同一條船<br />\n當然事後可以檢討<br />\n但發生個一下 <br />\n大家一定要齊上齊落</span></span>"},{"pid":"02c542647c1ca6519964f4b8c5d6e43132b87521","tid":1307822,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bc5fa7a131b0a62e599ef7663ee81492534d121","tid":1307822,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:15:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無論你選擇還手定係走佬<br />\n我地都會幫你說項 幫你spin<br />\n因為我地係同一條船<br />\n當然事後可以檢討<br />\n但發生個一下 <br />\n大家一定要齊上齊落</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:17:30.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"13596ac9fee5b121381be3dd1ed9ec487d4f33e1","tid":1307822,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:20:40.000Z","msg":"<img sr